There was a short nod from POLAR CLAW as he looked across the area
around the cave, cool optics surveying the terrain. &quot;Good.&quot; he said
after a moment.

&quot;There.&quot; WOLFGANG said as he pointed at the horizon as the shuttle was
already closing in our their position.

It took only a few minutes for the shuttle to begin landing
proceedures and drop to the ground. &quot;Polar Claw, Prowl and Wolfgang.&quot;
LORD ELDER nodded to each in turn. &quot;It has been some time.&quot;

&quot;Brother!&quot; WOLFGANG said as he walked up to LORD ELDER. They both
smiled as they came together and shookhands, extending it into a hug.
&quot;Yes it has been some time.&quot;

If one were paying attention both units looked very similar, with only
a few slight modifications and color variations. However LORD ELDER
did look signifigantly older than WOLFGANG.

&quot;What brings you here?&quot; ELDER said looking at POLAR CLAW. &quot;The recall?&quot;

POLAR CLAW nodded, &quot;It sounded urgent.&quot;

&quot;Come, help us get the Fuzors on the shuttle and we can all get back
to the Ark.&quot; ELDER said. He turned to TALON, &quot;it is good to see that
are among friends.&quot;

